name: #15. GARY "BENDS" MCKENNY
description:
If you're looking for a driver, "Bends" is your man. But you better hold on tight. Doesn't brake at the turns. Doesn't brake for nobody.

"The more you take, the more you leave behind. What am I?"
"Feed me and I live, yet give me a drink and I die"
"What has hands but can not clap?"
